{"id":1683093,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-28T12:44:06.324Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1683093,"imdb_id":"tt10342282","origin_country":["CH"],"original_language":"fr","original_title":"Gossliwil - Cinq Essais sur la culture paysanne et l'économie paysanne, sur le travail, la propriété et le temps","overview":"The film authors cautiously approach the village of Gossliwil in Bucheggberg, Solothurn, with its 160 inhabitants, and sift through traces of a rural culture of survival under modern conditions without romanticization. Knowledge of the destructive threat of industrialization and the mechanisms of a global food market for the farming world is included in the research. The farmers themselves have their say; at the same time, their tradition is traced in pictures, deliberate narrative rhythm, repetitions and sayings. The result is a clever analysis of Swiss agricultural policy, whose clear structure never slips into nostalgia; a highlight of Swiss documentary filmmaking.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":89375,"logo_path":null,"name":"Filmkollektiv Zürich AG","origin_country":"CH"}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"1985-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":232,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Gossliwil - Five Essays on Peasant Culture and Peasant Economy, on Work, Property and Time","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6171962,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Béatrice Leuthold-Michel","original_name":"Béatrice Leuthold-Michel","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"69ef7925914645f04a151824","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6171962,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Béatrice Leuthold-Michel","origin